## 💾 Database Schema

The database relies on MongoDB (via Mongoose) and consists of two primary collections.

### 1. User Schema ([user.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/server/models/user.js))
Represents a user account, tracking their personal info, virtual cash balance, and overall performance statistics.
* **`name`**: `String` (Required)
* **`email`**: `String` (Required)
* **`current_funds`**: `Number` (Default: `₹1,00,000` virtual funds)
* **`stocks`**: `ObjectId` (Ref: `Portfolio` model)
* **`realisedPL`**: `Number` (Default: `0` - Tracks total booked profit/loss from sales)
* **`netInvestment`**: `Number` (Default: `0` - Tracks total active investment)

### 2. Portfolio & Stock Schema ([stocks.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/server/models/stocks.js))
Tracks the stock holdings for each user.
* **`user`**: `ObjectId` (Ref: `user` model, Required)
* **`stocks`**: Array of sub-documents:
  * **`company`**: `String` (Required)
  * **`average_price`**: `Number` (Required)
  * **`quantity`**: `Number` (Required)

