## 🛡️ Middlewares

* **[isloggedin.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/server/middleware/isloggedin.js)**: Verifies the JWT cookie (`token`) using the key stored in `process.env.JWT`. Fetches user information from MongoDB and attaches the user object to `req.user`.
* **[order.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/server/middleware/order.js)**: Enforces real-world Indian Stock Market constraints (NSE Rules) on buy and sell actions:
  * **Weekend Check**: Rejects orders on Saturdays and Sundays.
  * **Holiday Check**: Rejects orders on a hardcoded list of NSE holidays for 2026.
  * **Market Hours Check**: Rejects orders placed outside standard hours **09:15 to 15:30 IST**.

