## 🎨 Frontend React Client

The frontend client resides in `client/` and communicates with the backend API via relative URLs (proxied to `http://localhost:5000` via [package.json](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/package.json)).

### Main Components:
1. **[App.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/src/App.js)**: Outlines routing using `react-router-dom` (`/`, `/markets`, `/portfolio`, `/stock-details`, `/profile`, `/ai`, `/about`, `/contact`).
2. **[Home.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/src/components/Home.js)**:
   * *Unauthenticated*: Shows a landing page promoting paper trading and virtual funds.
   * *Authenticated*: Renders the user Dashboard with KPI metrics (Portfolio Value, Realised P/L, Funds), mock activity feed, mock financial news, and navigation links.
3. **[Navbar.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/src/components/Navbar.js)**: Controls top navigation, Auth0 logins/logouts, displays virtual wallet balances, allows quick fund updates, and manages a search bar with auto-suggestions loading from `companyList.json`. Clicking a search result navigates to `/stock-details`.
4. **[Details.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/src/components/Details.js)**: Renders live NSE/BSE stock details, P/E, EPS, Market Cap, 52-week high/low progress bar, and a buy/sell trade panel.
5. **[Portfolio.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/src/components/Portfolio.js)**: Displays portfolio statistics (Unrealised P/L calculated using live prices, Holdings list). Users can trade (buy/sell) shares directly from individual stock cards.
6. **[Ai.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/src/components/Ai.js)**: Front-end for the `/aisuggest` backend. Users input budgets and query the AI Assistant.
7. **[Markets.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/StarkVest-main/client/src/components/Markets.js)**: Houses global asset tabs (Sensex, Nasdaq, Bitcoin, Gold) using a TradingView Advanced Chart widget.

